# PoseFlow Project Update

I have successfully renamed the project from "YogaBuddy/OneBreath" to **PoseFlow** and set up the infrastructure for GitHub Pages deployment.

## Changes Made

### Renaming
- Updated all occurrences of "YogaBuddy" and "OneBreath" to **PoseFlow** in:
  - [one-breath-app/index.html](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/one-breath-app/index.html) (Title, Meta tags)
  - [one-breath-app/src/components/StartupAnimation.tsx](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/one-breath-app/src/components/StartupAnimation.tsx) (Hero title)
  - [one-breath-app/src/components/OnboardingPage.tsx](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/one-breath-app/src/components/OnboardingPage.tsx) (Welcome text)
  - [one-breath-app/public/breathbox-meditation/index.html](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/one-breath-app/public/breathbox-meditation/index.html) (Meditation page title)
  - [one-breath-app/start.sh](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/one-breath-app/start.sh) and [one-breath-app/README.md](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/one-breath-app/README.md) (Project documentation)

### Deployment Setup
- **Vite Configuration**: Updated [vite.config.ts](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/one-breath-app/vite.config.ts) with `base: "/YogaBuddy/"` to ensure assets load correctly on GitHub Pages under the `YogaBuddy` repository.
- **GitHub Actions**: Created a deployment workflow at [.github/workflows/deploy.yml](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/.github/workflows/deploy.yml). This will automatically build and deploy your app to the `gh-pages` branch whenever you push to `main`.

